title: Ethan Got Covid, Jordan Peterson Publicly Humiliated - Off The Rails #41
description: Today we return from a COVID hiatus! Ethan had an unfortunate birthday surprise that had him locked in the basement the last week, so we recap his experience in the brig. We also celebrate Dan's 5 year anniversary on the podcast, go over the biggest Jordan Peterson mask off moment yet, and much more!
